net.java.jddac.jmdi.comm
Class MessageAttr

java.lang.Object
  net.java.jddac.jmdi.comm.MessageAttr

public class MessageAttr
extends java.lang.Object

Attributes for XML encoded network messages. Although any arbitrary string can be used as an attribute name, these are "well-known" attribute names that the infrastructure knows how to handle.
